This configuration will function correctly but only for load currents up to around 25 mA, which is the maximum output current capability of the 741 op amp as per the data sheets. If the load (denoted as LD) attempts to draw a current $I_{L}$ exceeding this limit, the output voltage will drop, and regulation will be lost.

